{
  "stem": "4189.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were able to take that bottom out and hide it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So this way, we were not caught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, there was another thing that-- another incident that I want to mention in Auschwitz, that was the-- they were the women that were working in there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, there was a group of women that were working in a bunker that was outside the factory-- just a little bit away from the factory.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was a bunker halfway underground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In that bunker they stored the dynamite that was used in that spark plug.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "See, the spark plug had to have a small amount of dynamite, which was-- which ignited on impact, and then exploded this whole thing and blew up the tank.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So this dynamite was stored in that bunker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the women that were working in there, they had to take out just enough dynamite for every tour-- for every day tour to bring into the factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because they didn't want to store all this dynamite inside the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the women had this dynamite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, then, there was another kommando-- which was called the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Sonderkommando was a kommando that worked in the crematoria where they burned all the bodies that were gassed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these people, what they did-- the-- the SS took these people that worked there, about 400 of them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The kommando consisted of 400 prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every once in a while, they would take all these people and kill them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they did not-- and put new ones in there-- new prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they did not want them to know how many people were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, because they saw that on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
